data.description: Introducing a stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom family home nestled in the picturesque Moss Bluff community. This spacious property boasts a generous .58-acre lot in an established neighborhood just off of Sam Houston Jones Parkway. The exterior welcomes you with beautiful landscaping, complete with a stone border, rock bed, and a collection of eye-catching trees including crape myrtle, red maple, and weeping willow. A charming front porch featuring cedar posts and stained shutters sets the tone for the warm and inviting atmosphere within. Step inside to discover new tile flooring throughout the foyer, dining room, two bedrooms, and upstairs hallway. A cozy wood-burning fireplace with a black walnut mantel serves as the centerpiece of the living area, while the gourmet kitchen offers ample counter space and a convenient island with room for four barstools. Additional features include a new dishwasher, a breakfast area, and an upstairs guest bathroom that has been tastefully remodeled. All oversized bedrooms are fitted with walk-in closets, while the master suite boasts two walk-in closets and a large bathroom ready to be transformed into a luxury suite. A quaint room at the top of the staircase is equipped with a closet and being used as a bedroom but used to serve as an upstairs laundry room and still has the washer and dryer hookups. The property also includes new garage doors, an extra-long garage perfect for a workspace, and a bonus room above the garage that can be remodeled into a heated and cooled space. AC units have a parts warranty until 2027, roof is warranted until 2030, siding and gutter repair is warranted until 2026, upstairs bathroom plumbing work is warranted until 2026, and brand-new garage doors have a 3-year warranty; all warranties can be transferred to new buyers. Finishing touches such as freshly painted front door, crown molding, and trim throughout the house, a rod iron staircase, and a covered back patio elevate this property to a truly exceptional home. Don't miss this opportunity to experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and space in Moss Bluff.
